lead_paragraph: Two David Silva goals gave new Spain coach Julen Lopetegui the ideal start with a 2-0 win that ensured a tough debut for his Belgium counterpart Roberto Martinez in a friendly on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Silva Double Gives Spain Win Over Belgium Under New Coaches
